## Part 3 Changelog
Added a few pictures in the 'gallery page'
Added a timestamp in the footer sections for all the pages for a good user experience
Added a  realtime date stamp  in the header section of the home page
Added a gallery lightbox  for the images in the gallery page to improve the experience if the users.
Created an enquiry page as well as the enquiry form
Added javascript form validation rules for the user input
Applied a css layout on the enquiry form
Added a feedback functionality for submission of the form
Customized the layoutof the dynamic contentin the css file
Implemented javascript interactive accordion buttons on the "service" page for the (Our services, Nails section, nails services,Eye lashes section, lashes services,Maintenance and why choose us) content.
 


